<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">

<head>
  <title>Dressmify - Home</title>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    /* General Reset and Fonts */
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');
    
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    :root {
      /* Nuova palette di colori professionale */
      --primary: #5048E5;
      --primary-dark: #3832A0;
      --primary-light: #F3F2FF;
      --secondary: #0EA5E9;
      --accent: #16BDCA;
      --dark: #111827;
      --gray-dark: #374151;
      --gray: #9CA3AF;
      --gray-light: #F9FAFB;
      --white: #FFFFFF;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      background-color: var(--gray-light);
      color: var(--dark);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      padding-top: 80px;
      position: relative;
    }

    /* Elegant Patterns */
    .bg-pattern {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background-image: 
        radial-gradient(rgba(80, 72, 229, 0.03) 2px, transparent 2px),
        radial-gradient(rgba(80, 72, 229, 0.02) 2px, transparent 2px);
      background-size: 40px 40px;
      background-position: 0 0, 20px 20px;
      z-index: -2;
    }

    /* Navbar Styling */
    .navbar {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: var(--white);
      padding: 16px 0;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.05);
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .navbar-container {
      width: 92%;
      max-width: 1400px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .navbar-brand {
      font-size: 1.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--primary);
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .navbar-brand i {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-right: 10px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }
    
    .navbar-brand span {
      position: relative;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    
    .navbar-brand span::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -4px;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--secondary), transparent);
    }

    .navbar-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .navbar a {
      color: var(--gray-dark);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .navbar a i {
      margin-right: 8px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .navbar a:hover {
      background-color: var(--primary-light);
      color: var(--primary);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .navbar a.active {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
      color: var(--white);
    }

    /* Main Content */
    main {
      max-width: 1400px;
      width: 92%;
      margin: 40px auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      position: relative;
    }

    /* Hero Section */
    .hero-section {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--white), var(--primary-light));
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 0;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(80, 72, 229, 0.1);
      position: relative;
      min-height: 400px;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }
    
    .hero-content {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 60px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    
    .hero-image {
      flex: 1;
      position: relative;
      min-height: 400px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .hero-image-overlay {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(80, 72, 229, 0.8), rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.7));
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    
    .hero-image-icon {
      font-size: 10rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      transform: rotate(-5deg);
    }
    
    .circle-decoration {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    
    .circle-1 {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
      background: radial-gradient(var(--secondary), transparent 70%);
      opacity: 0.05;
      top: -100px;
      right: 10%;
    }
    
    .circle-2 {
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
      background: radial-gradient(var(--accent), transparent 70%);
      opacity: 0.04;
      bottom: -50px;
      left: 30%;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: var(--dark);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      position: relative;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    
    h1::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      height: 4px;
      width: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
      bottom: -10px;
      left: 0;
      border-radius: 30px;
    }

    .hero-text {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--gray-dark);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 35px;
      max-width: 80%;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: var(--primary);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* Buttons */
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
      color: white;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(80, 72, 229, 0.2);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .btn i {
      margin-right: 10px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(80, 72, 229, 0.25);
    }
    
    .btn:hover i {
      transform: translateX(3px);
    }

    /* Features Section */
    .features-section {
      position: relative;
      padding: 30px 0;
    }

    .section-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 50px;
    }

    .feature-heading {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: var(--dark);
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .feature-subheading {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--gray-dark);
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .features-container {
      display: flex;
      gap: 30px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .feature-card {
      flex: 1;
      background-color: var(--white);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.05);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .feature-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 4px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    }

    .feature-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.1);
    }
    
    .feature-card:hover::before {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    .feature-icon {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: var(--primary-light);
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .feature-icon::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(80, 72, 229, 0.2), rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1));
      border-radius: 20px;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .feature-card:hover .feature-icon::after {
      opacity: 1;
    }
    
    .feature-icon i {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .feature-title {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: var(--dark);
    }

    .feature-desc {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--gray-dark);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media (max-width: 1100px) {
      .hero-section {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      
      .hero-content {
        padding: 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      
      .hero-text {
        max-width: 100%;
      }
      
      h1::after {
        left: 25%;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .features-container {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      
      .feature-card {
        max-width: 100%;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .navbar-container {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      
      .navbar-brand {
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      
      .navbar-links {
        width: 100%;
        justify-content: space-around;
      }
      
      .navbar a {
        padding: 10px 14px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
      
      h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 576px) {
      .navbar-links {
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 5px;
      }
      
      .navbar a {
        padding: 8px 12px;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }
      
      .navbar a i {
        margin-right: 6px;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
      
      h1 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
      }
      
      .hero-content {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      
      .btn {
        padding: 12px 24px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <!-- Background Pattern -->
  <div class="bg-pattern"></div>

  <div class="navbar">
    <div class="navbar-container">
      <a href="/home" class="navbar-brand">
        <i class="fas fa-tshirt"></i>
        <span>Dressmify</span>
      </a>
      <div class="navbar-links">
        <a href="/home" class="active"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> <span>Home</span></a>
        <a href="/noleggio"><i class="fas fa-tshirt"></i> <span>Noleggio</span></a>
        <a href="/static/index.html"><i class="fas fa-comments"></i> <span>Chat</span></a>
        <a href="/logout"><i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i> <span>Logout</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <main>
    <section class="hero-section">
      <div class="circle-decoration circle-1"></div>
      <div class="circle-decoration circle-2"></div>
      
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>Welcome Back</h1>
        <p class="hero-text">{{message}}</p>
        <a href="/noleggio" class="btn">
          <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
          Esplora i Servizi
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="hero-image">
        <div class="hero-image-overlay">
          <i class="fas fa-tshirt hero-image-icon"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="feature-heading">Dressmify: La moda a portata di click</h2>
        <p class="feature-subheading">Dressmify è la piattaforma innovativa che ti consente di noleggiare capi d'abbigliamento di alta qualità per ogni occasione, risparmiando e rispettando l'ambiente.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="features-container">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-tshirt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Noleggio Smart</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">Accedi a un guardaroba infinito di capi firmati, pagando solo per il tempo che li utilizzi.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Sostenibilità</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">Riduci il tuo impatto ambientale scegliendo il noleggio invece dell'acquisto di nuovi capi.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Qualità Premium</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">Solo capi selezionati dei migliori brand, controllati e igienizzati dopo ogni utilizzo.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>

</html>